parameters:
It seems like this magic circle can enhance our
detection abilities.

Yeah. My magical power has recovered more than I
expected, so it seems like I can use detection
magic.
Do you feel it that strongly?

Yeah... It's a magical power unlike anything I've
ever felt before.

Since she possesses the power of the king, it must
be quite substantial.

I feel it a little higher from here... around the
area of the club building.

Yesterday, Amelia was taken away in the club
building, right?
Is that where their base is?
But there was nothing else besides Amelia, right?

I wonder if there's anywhere in the club building
that we haven't searched yet.

By the way, what exactly is the Student Council
President?

I didn't know there was anyone else besides the
Vice President and Senior Jackson who is that
strong.

That person is from the Martin family, and it
seems their ancestors captured Leviathan.

The goal is to obtain Leviathan's magical power
and dominate this world.

It seems that the current Student Council
President has taken quite a bit of power from
Leviathan.

I don't know their original strength, but I think
they are quite strong.
This is a pretty bad situation, huh?

Ah, that's why there's no time. Since I carry over
my memories like you, I don't want to loop
anymore.

But I know the whereabouts of the Student Council
President. All that's left is to defeat them,
right?
What will happen to Leviathan if we defeat her?

Yesterday, I couldn't ask about the details of the
contract.

The condition to use the time reversal magic is to
find and defeat the one who has imprisoned
Leviathan.

So if we defeat the student council president, the
contract will be completed.

The magic barrier that is imprisoning Leviathan
will also disappear.

Ah, but I don't think Leviathan is that much of a
bad demon.

We've spent quite a lot of time together, but it
seems like you're not interested in invasion or
anything.
Can we trust the words of a demon?

What Hiyo is saying is correct... but I think
there is a possibility for dialogue.
I want you to trust me now.

There's nothing we can do against the Demon King
anyway.

Even if we call for help from the Hero Association
now, it will take time for them to arrive.

Leviathan's combat abilities are only enough to be
captured by students.
I don't think she's that strong.
What about the magic to turn back time?

It takes time to activate, so if we engage in
battle, I won't be able to use it.

Besides, I can carry over my memories. I won't let
Leviathan have her way.

If anything happens, please take care of it,
Masamune-san.

Although I don't think there's anything, she's
quite straightforward.
I can't imagine the Demon King...
But, I also feel like I want to give it a try.

Ah, once everything is resolved, I'll try to meet
everyone too.

So, we must definitely defeat the Student Council
President.
Let's go to the club building.
